Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.37,0:22:25.72,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}運命は絶望?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.74,0:22:28.32,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}それとも希望?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.65,0:22:34.77,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}ゆらぎの中で  受信してゆく
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.79,0:22:36.91,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}悲しみにも負けない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.93,0:22:39.60,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}勇気だけをください
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.07,0:22:45.85,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}大切なもの  守るため
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.92,0:22:51.26,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}「強さ」はあると信じてる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.28,0:22:57.12,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}Saving our future　一緒に
