Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.93,0:22:39.60,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}不會向悲傷低頭的勇氣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.07,0:22:45.85,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}為了保護珍貴的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.92,0:22:51.26,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}我相信自己的堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.28,0:22:57.12,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}Saving our future  讓我們一同
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.39,0:23:00.28,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}敞開明天的門  向開闊的天空
